Implementation plans for this project live in docs/plans/. When I give you a plan:
- Follow it exactly. Do not add features, files, or abstractions it doesn't specify.
- Treat the "Guardrails for Cursor (DO NOT list)" section as hard constraints.
- Keep middleware.ts edge-safe (no @/lib/* imports).
- When you're done, report the exact files you changed and confirm the build/typecheck passes.
If something in the plan seems wrong or a build error contradicts it, stop and tell me with the exact error — do not improvise a workaround.